  "3014580": {
    "name": "Follow Us",
    "steam_appid": 3014580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/940dee34e6599fa0e1df7b06baaca700.poster.avif?t=1771329904\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/940dee34e6599fa0e1df7b06baaca700.webm?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/940dee34e6599fa0e1df7b06baaca700.mp4?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不久的将来，人类完全生活在屏幕中的世界，外出已经变得极其危险。<br>你在为一个名为“Follow Us”的地下频道进行直播，并要不惜一切代价留住观众。<br>你的任务：取悦观众…并且活下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>Follow Us</i>》是一款<strong>非对称双人合作恐怖游戏</strong>。在这场既搞笑又惊悚的“关系压力测试”中，<strong>一名玩家负责</strong>在阴森的环境中<strong>探索</strong>，<strong>另一名玩家则负责</strong>在厢式货车内进行远程<strong>指引</strong>，努力让搭档活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/40fc12837370bdfc728f3718e7e23074.avif?t=1771329904\" width=1560 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/e296e7e4b2fc4546403bc084d55556ce.poster.avif?t=1771329904\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/e296e7e4b2fc4546403bc084d55556ce.webm?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/e296e7e4b2fc4546403bc084d55556ce.mp4?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局游戏，玩家都可以自由选择角色，要么扮演无畏的<strong>探索者</strong>，勇敢穿越灵异事件频发的致命地图；要么作为<strong>操控者</strong>，留在后方指引队友，并黑入游戏场景提供保护。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的非对称机制，完美适配具有不同喜好的玩家：喜欢刺激的玩笑可以尽情享受被惊吓的快感；而喜欢休闲的玩家则可以通过远程指挥，获得虽然混乱但相对轻松的体验。无论你的哪种玩家，都能在其中获得乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/e0d52747535823bf951fed63fdba147b.avif?t=1771329904\" width=1560 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/786bf384a87931e2c38b6578bdf8a08b.poster.avif?t=1771329904\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/786bf384a87931e2c38b6578bdf8a08b.webm?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/786bf384a87931e2c38b6578bdf8a08b.mp4?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>Follow Us</i>》摒弃了复杂的操作机制，<strong>以沟通作为核心玩法</strong>。游戏通过将“孤立无援”与“同伴联络”这两种截然不同的体验结合在一起，营造出了强烈的紧张感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个任务都是对友谊与亲密关系的<strong>实时压力测试</strong>。好友或情侣在角色互换与权力交替时，往往会产生意想不到的笑料和惊吓反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/c5c4a4c61e3b7fe8b05868dec2a3c107.avif?t=1771329904\" width=1560 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/7e268f37e19a81c93e958ddf566e4787.poster.avif?t=1771329904\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/7e268f37e19a81c93e958ddf566e4787.webm?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014580/extras/7e268f37e19a81c93e958ddf566e4787.mp4?t=1771329904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的每个关卡都对应着<strong>不同类型的恐惧</strong>，从心理压抑到纯粹惊悚。探索者会在现场直面孤独与危险，操控者则需要承受无力感与持续高压的双重折磨。每一次角色互换，都会带来全新的情感体验，让每局游戏都独一无二。意料之外的沟通冲突，必将制造出令人毛骨悚然的合作混乱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会把自己的性命托付给谁？</p>",
